{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01Rn44ToeGtfWTj1hJvDZDEy","type":"tool_result","content":"1\t# Session Issues Log — 2026-04-03\n2\t\n3\t### 4-3-trace-id-generation-injection — create-story (2026-04-03T00:25)\n4\t\n5\t- **Risk: `trace_ids` field on WorkflowState** — adding optional field requires updating `isValidWorkflowState()`. Made optional to avoid breaking existing states.\n6\t- All 9 ACs are test-provable. Pure logic module with no I/O.\n7\t\n8\t## Token Report\n9\t- Total tool calls: 14\n10\t- By tool: Bash: 1, Read: 5, Grep: 4, Write: 1, Glob: 3\n11\t\n12\t### 4-3-trace-id-generation-injection — dev-story (2026-04-03T00:30)\n13\t\n14\tNone.\n15\t\n16\t## Token Report\n17\t- Total tool calls: 14\n18\t- By tool: Read: 5, Edit: 6, Write: 2, Bash: 4, Glob: 1\n19\t\n20\t### 4-3-trace-id-generation-injection — code-review (2026-04-03T00:37)\n21\t\n22\t**Bugs found:**\n23\t- HIGH: `generateTraceId` accepted NaN/Infinity/negative/float iteration values. Fixed.\n24\t- MEDIUM: No segment length cap — unbounded trace IDs. Fixed.\n25\t- MEDIUM: `formatTracePrompt('')` silently produced empty trace marker. Fixed.\n26\t- MEDIUM: `workflow-state.ts` coverage at 79.06%, below 80% floor. Fixed with 10 new tests.\n27\t\n28\t**LOW (not fixed):** duplicate trace ID guard missing; empty runId+taskName produces ugly ID; sanitizeSegment strips non-ASCII.\n29\t\n30\t## Token Report\n31\t- Total tool calls: 23\n32\t- By tool: Bash: 12, Read: 7, Edit: 5, Glob: 2, Skill: 1\n33\t"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"1d3ed03d-179a-4015-85c3-0be0521b6265","uuid":"70b4991f-163b-429e-9d35-06a3a831b425","timestamp":"2026-04-02T20:56:04.262Z","tool_use_result":{"type":"text","file":{"filePath":"/Users/ivintik/dev/personal/codeharness/_bmad-output/implementation-artifacts/.session-issues.md","content":"# Session Issues Log — 2026-04-03\n\n### 4-3-trace-id-generation-injection — create-story (2026-04-03T00:25)\n\n- **Risk: `trace_ids` field on WorkflowState** — adding optional field requires updating `isValidWorkflowState()`. Made optional to avoid breaking existing states.\n- All 9 ACs are test-provable. Pure logic module with no I/O.\n\n## Token Report\n- Total tool calls: 14\n- By tool: Bash: 1, Read: 5, Grep: 4, Write: 1, Glob: 3\n\n### 4-3-trace-id-generation-injection — dev-story (2026-04-03T00:30)\n\nNone.\n\n## Token Report\n- Total tool calls: 14\n- By tool: Read: 5, Edit: 6, Write: 2, Bash: 4, Glob: 1\n\n### 4-3-trace-id-generation-injection — code-review (2026-04-03T00:37)\n\n**Bugs found:**\n- HIGH: `generateTraceId` accepted NaN/Infinity/negative/float iteration values. Fixed.\n- MEDIUM: No segment length cap — unbounded trace IDs. Fixed.\n- MEDIUM: `formatTracePrompt('')` silently produced empty trace marker. Fixed.\n- MEDIUM: `workflow-state.ts` coverage at 79.06%, below 80% floor. Fixed with 10 new tests.\n\n**LOW (not fixed):** duplicate trace ID guard missing; empty runId+taskName produces ugly ID; sanitizeSegment strips non-ASCII.\n\n## Token Report\n- Total tool calls: 23\n- By tool: Bash: 12, Read: 7, Edit: 5, Glob: 2, Skill: 1\n","numLines":33,"startLine":1,"totalLines":33}}}
