t-resolver.ts             # Agent config resolution, SDK compilation\n314-│   │   ├── workflow-engine.ts            # Flow execution, loops, finding injection\n315-│   │   ├── agent-dispatch.ts             # Agent SDK query(), sessions, trace IDs\n316:│   │   ├── evaluator.ts                  # Blind evaluator workspace + spawn + verdict parsing\n317-│   │   ├── circuit-breaker.ts            # Score-based stagnation detection (TS rewrite)\n318-│   │   ├── workflow-state.ts             # State persistence, crash recovery (replaces state.ts)\n319-│   │   │\n--\n336-│   │   ├── epic-generator.ts             # REWORK — strip beads gap-IDs, keep epic generation\n337-│   │   ├── onboard-checks.ts            # REWORK — strip beads calls, keep preconditions\n338-│   │   ├── deps.ts                        # REWORK — remove showboat/beads deps\n339:│   │   ├── verify-env.ts                 # REWORK — evolve into evaluator workspace setup\n340-│   │   │\n341-│   │   └── __tests__/                     # Co-located unit tests (update with source)\n342-│   │\n--\n417-| `src/lib/epic-generator.ts` | `appendGapId`, beads calls | Epic generation from scan |\n418-| `src/lib/onboard-checks.ts` | Beads precondition checks | Non-beads preconditions |\n419-| `src/lib/deps.ts` | Showboat/beads dep installation | Claude, Docker dep checks |\n420:| `src/lib/verify-env.ts` | Old verifier workspace logic | Evolve into evaluator workspace |\n421-| `src/commands/bridge.ts` | `createIssue`, `listIssues` imports | BMAD story bridge logic |\n422-| `src/commands/init.ts` | Beads init, hook installation | Stack detect, workflow generation |\n423-| `src/commands/onboard.ts` | Beads calls from epic-generator | Scanning, epic generation |\n--\n491-        agent-dispatch: SDK query() → agent works → returns\n492-        workflow-state: write checkpoint\n493-    → per-run tasks (verify):\n494:        evaluator: setup workspace → agent-dispatch → parse verdict\n495-        workflow-state: write checkpoint