dy removed, no error\n\n- [ ] Task 5: Verify existing integration points (AC: #4, #8)\n  - [ ] Confirm `templates/agents/evaluator.yaml` has `disallowedTools: [Edit, Write]` (from story 3-2)\n  - [ ] Confirm `agent-dispatch.ts` line 134 already passes `options.cwd` to `query()` (from story 4-1)\n  - [ ] Confirm `compileSubagentDefinition()` in `agent-resolver.ts` already passes `disallowedTools` through (line 343)\n  - [ ] No changes needed to `agent-dispatch.ts` or `agent-resolver.ts`\n\n- [ ] Task 6: Write unit tests (AC: #9)\n  - [ ] Create `src/lib/__tests__/source-isolation.test.ts`\n  - [ ] Test: `createIsolatedWorkspace()` creates temp dir with expected structure\n  - [ ] Test: story files are copied to `story-files/` subdirectory\n  - [ ] Test: `src/` directory does NOT exist in isolated workspace\n  - [ ] Test: `toDispatchOptions()` returns `{ cwd }` pointing to the temp dir\n  - [ ] Test: `cleanup()` removes the temp directory\n  - [ ] Test: `cleanup()` called twice does not throw (idempotent)\n  - [ ] Test: empty `storyFiles` array creates directories but no files in `story-files/`\n  - [ ] Test: missing story file logs a warning and is skipped\n  - [ ] Test: `verdict/` directory exists in workspace\n  - [ ] Verify 80%+ coverage on `source-isolation.ts`","new_string":"- [x] Task 1: Create source isolation module interfaces (AC: #1, #3)\n  - [x] Create `src/lib/source-isolation.ts`\n  - [x] Define `IsolationOptions` interface: `{ runId: string; storyFiles: string[] }`\n  - [x] Define `IsolatedWorkspace` interface: `{ dir: string; storyFilesDir: string; verdictDir: string; toDispatchOptions(): DispatchOptions; cleanup(): Promise<void> }`\n  - [x] Import `DispatchOptions` from `agent-dispatch.ts` for return type\n\n- [x] Task 2: Implement workspace creation (AC: #1, #2, #6)\n  - [x] Implement `createIsolatedWorkspace(options: IsolationOptions): Promise<IsolatedWorkspace>`\n  - [x] Create temp directory at `/tmp/codeharness-verify-{runId}/` using `mkdtemp` or