ace`, `IsolationOptions`, `IsolatedWorkspace` |\n\nAnd update the file count from 59 to 60.\n\nDo NOT ask questions. Do NOT run git commands. Do NOT modify sprint-status.yaml.\n\nMANDATORY — End with `## Session Issues` and `## Token Report` sections."}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_015UHexPBr7C4j7cQ2rdJdyp","session_id":"1d3ed03d-179a-4015-85c3-0be0521b6265","uuid":"205199f8-2155-44ce-bc9b-540049b38c61","timestamp":"2026-04-02T21:24:58.755Z"}
